    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total stunner. This car has been pampered since day one\u2014always garaged, meticulously detailed, and it seriously looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! Not a single blemish to be found. It drives like a dream and still has that 'new car' feel. I\u2019m looking for a buyer who will love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014you've gotta see this one in person! \u2728",
