    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a concours-level 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS. This example is mechanically flawless, with the critical rod bearing service and rear subframe reinforcement already completed to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile, short-throw shifts, delivering power through a factory-spec variable M differential lock. The suspension maintains its original geometry with no bushing deflection, and the undercarriage is free of oxidation or fluid seepage. This is a turn-key machine for the purist, exhibiting perfect compression across all cylinders and a pristine, factory-correct aesthetic. A rare opportunity to acquire a peak-era M-car in its most desirable mechanical state.",
      "price": 46500.0,
