    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster with a professional-grade ceramic coating applied last season; there are absolutely no rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings to be found. Every body panel is original with matching VIN tags. Inside, the cabin remains in 'time capsule' state\u2014the leather upholstery is supple with no bolster wear, the dashboard is free of UV damage, and it still carries that distinct new-car scent. All electronic components, from the high-fidelity sound system to the dual-zone climate control, function perfectly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It comes with a binder of exhaustive service records from the same certified master technician. Recent preventative maintenance includes a full fluid flush and a fresh set of premium performance tires. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade investment for the discerning driver who demands perfection.",
